//[Reference] 'Oh, hello ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10000100=あら、こんにちは^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'How is everything these days? I heard you were working with ^c:1486b0;Aliza^c:pop; on some interesting things?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10000200=最近どう？^c:1486b0;アリザ^c:pop;と面白いことをやってるって聞いたけど？
//[Reference] 'Seems you were the one who managed to secure some of the resources I used for my latest experiment too!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10000300=私の新しい実験に使った資源を確保してくれたのもあなただったのね！
//[Reference] 'Hmm, is that an ^c:d03e37;airship blueprint^c:pop; you have there? How about I take a look?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10000400=あら、あなたが持ってるのは^c:d03e37;飛行船の設計図^c:pop;かしら？ちょっと見せてくれない？
//[Reference] 'No, no. This isn't going to work like that...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10000500=ダメダメね。これじゃ動かないわ…
//[Reference] 'You can't just remove parts and expect it to go faster. That would just compromise stability!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10000600=部品を外すだけじゃ速度は期待できないわよ。それだと安定性を損なうだけよ！
//[Reference] 'Here, this might be a better path to follow, but there are still some fundamental problems...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10000700=はいどうぞ、順番通りにやった方が良いかもしれないけど、まだ根本的な問題があるわ…
//[Reference] 'You can't just break the laws of physics!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10000800=物理法則をただ破ることはできないわ！
//[Reference] 'Airships don't run on magic you know! It doesn't exist!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10000900=だからって魔法で飛行船は動かないし！って魔法なんてある訳ないでしょ！
//[Reference] 'But...say it did exist...it would probably be the key to circumventing the flaws...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10001000=でも…存在していたらしいの…きっとそれが現状を打破する鍵になるでしょうね…
//[Reference] 'Hello there, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10001100=こんにちは、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'I've been in this village for quite some time now but I've yet to see many scientific advancements.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10001200=結構長いことこの村にいるけど、科学の進歩はあまり見受けられないわね。
//[Reference] 'I suspect this is largely due to the inadequate facilities available for research and development.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10001300=研究や開発に使えそうな設備の不足が主な原因じゃないかしら。
//[Reference] 'After much careful consideration, I have decided to enlist your aid in rectifying the situation.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10001400=検討を重ねた結果、現状を打開するためにあなたに救援を要請するわ。
//[Reference] 'You will help me, won't you, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10001500=助けてくれるわよね、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;？
//[Reference] 'Of course!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10001600=もちろん！
//[Reference] 'Maybe some other time.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10001700=まあそのうちね。
//[Reference] 'Ah. I hadn't considered this outcome.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10001800=あら。この結果は考えてなかったわ。
//[Reference] 'I'll have to think on it some more...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10001900=もう少し検討する必要があるわね…
//[Reference] 'Great! I wouldn't have expected any less from you, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10002000=さっすが！あなたならそう言ってくれると思ってたわ、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'So, first steps, first steps...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10002100=それじゃあ、まずは、まずはえーと…
//[Reference] 'Right! I suppose I'll need to get a permit for the establishment of a ^c:1486b0;lab^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10002200=そう！^c:1486b0;研究室^c:pop;の建設許可を貰わないといけないわ。
//[Reference] 'Wouldn't want to be conducting dangerous experiments without permission to do so!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10002300=許可なく危険な実験をするわけにはいかないからね！
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;Max^c:pop; would be absolutely furious!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10002400=^c:1486b0;マックス^c:pop;なら絶対に激怒するわ！
//[Reference] 'So how about you go see ^c:1486b0;Max^c:pop; and convince him to let us turn my home into a ^c:1486b0;lab^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10002500=だから私の家を^c:1486b0;研究室^c:pop;に改装できるように^c:1486b0;マックス^c:pop;を説得してきてくれないかしら？
//[Reference] 'You got the ^c:d03e37;permit^c:pop; then? Excellent!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10002600=^c:d03e37;許可^c:pop;を貰えたの？やったわ！
//[Reference] 'I've already begun documenting all the ^c:1486b0;machines^c:pop; I'm going to need for my experiments.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10002700=実験に必要な^c:1486b0;マシン^c:pop;は全て資料にまとめてあるわ。
//[Reference] 'These should tell you everything you need to know to get the place built!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10002800=これがあれば建設に必要な物が全て分かるはずよ！
//[Reference] 'I've thought hard about it, and I think you should expand ^c:1486b0;my home^c:pop; to accommodate them.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10002900=真面目に考えたんだけど、それが置けるくらいに^c:1486b0;私の家^c:pop;を広げてくれないかしら。
//[Reference] 'So basically, get them made and install them in ^c:1486b0;my home^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10003000=要するに、マシンを作ったら^c:1486b0;私の家^c:pop;に設置するのよ！
//[Reference] 'Any luck getting that ^c:d03e37;permit^c:pop; from ^c:1486b0;Max^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10003100=^c:1486b0;マックス^c:pop;から^c:d03e37;許可^c:pop;は貰えたかしら？
//[Reference] 'I don't really want to start construction without his permission...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10003200=彼の許可無しに建設を始めたくはないわ…
//[Reference] 'But I will if I have to!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10003300=でもいざとなったらやるわ！
//[Reference] 'I trust the blueprints I supplied were detailed enough?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10003400=渡した設計図は十分に分かりやすかったでしょ？
//[Reference] 'I hope I'm not going to be in the way too much while you perform the renovations!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10003500=改装中はあまり邪魔しないようにするわね！
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! It's a ^c:1486b0;lab^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10003600=^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！^c:1486b0;研究室^c:pop;だわ！
//[Reference] 'Ahh...that satisfying thrum of electrical motion...how have I slept without it?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10003700=ああぁ…電気振動の音で心が満たされるわ…もうこれなしでは眠れないかもね？
//[Reference] 'I'll be sure to let you know how my experiments proceed!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10003800=実験の進捗状況は絶対に報告するわ！
//[Reference] 'I hope that I'll be able to come up with some satisfactory results!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10003900=満足のいく結果が出せるといいな！
//[Reference] 'Until then, good luck with the farm!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10004000=それまでは、農業を頑張ってね！
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! It's a disaster!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10004100=^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！もう最悪よ！
//[Reference] 'I was experimenting with my microwave when something terrible happened...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10004200=電子レンジで実験をしてたらとんでもないことが起きちゃって…
//[Reference] 'I won't go into details on the experiment itself. Suffice to say it would have changed the world had it succeeded...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10004300=実験の詳細は割愛させてもらうけど。あえて言うなら、成功すれば世界を変革できたかもね…
//[Reference] 'But it didn't. It exploded instead. And now ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; is off cowering in a corner...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10004400=でも駄目だったわ。代わりに爆発しちゃうし。しかも^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;は部屋の隅で震えてるし…
//[Reference] 'I want to make him ^c:d03e37;a gift^c:pop; as an apology...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10004500=それで彼にお詫びとして^c:d03e37;プレゼント^c:pop;を贈りたいんだけど…
//[Reference] 'Do you think I could trouble you to make some ^c:d03e37;machine parts^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10004600=手間をかけさせちゃうけど^c:d03e37;マシンの部品^c:pop;を作ってもらえないかしら？
//[Reference] 'One ^c:d03e37;Machine Screen^c:pop;, two ^c:d03e37;Machine Cells^c:pop;, and a ^c:d03e37;Machine Sapper^c:pop; should do it.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10004700=^c:d03e37;マシンの画面^c:pop;を1つと、^c:d03e37;マシンの電池^c:pop;を2つ、あと^c:d03e37;マシンのサッパー^c:pop;を1つお願いするわ。
//[Reference] 'That was quicker than I expected, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10004800=思ったより早かったわね、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'How do you manage to work so fast? Some of those parts can take me weeks to make myself!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10004900=どうやったらそんなに早く済ませられるの？私でも作るのに数週間はかかる部品もあるのに！
//[Reference] 'I'll get to work on fixing everything up. In the meantime, feel free to go about your daily business.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10005000=私はこれを全て取り付ける作業に入るわ。あなたは存分に自分の日課をこなすといいわ。
//[Reference] 'There isn't much more you can do here right now.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10005100=もうここにいても、あなたのやれることは特に無いわね。
//[Reference] 'I really want to apologise properly to ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop;...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10005200=本当に、^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;にちゃんと謝りたいの…
//[Reference] 'Could you make me one ^c:d03e37;Machine Screen^c:pop;, two ^c:d03e37;Machine Cells^c:pop;, and a ^c:d03e37;Machine Sapper^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10005300=^c:d03e37;マシンの画面^c:pop;を1つと、^c:d03e37;マシンの電池^c:pop;を2つ、あと^c:d03e37;マシンのサッパー^c:pop;を1つ作ってくれないかしら？
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! It's a miracle!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10005400=^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！奇跡だわ！
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;Max^c:pop; seems to have forgiven us already!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10005500=^c:1486b0;マックス^c:pop;がもう許してくれたみたい！
//[Reference] 'I also managed to finish preparing ^c:1486b0;Leif's^c:pop; gift. Maybe you could deliver it for me?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10005600=私も^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;のプレゼントを用意できたところよ。私の代わりに届けてくれるかしら？
//[Reference] 'Quickly, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10005700=急いでね、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'I don't want to leave ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; cowering in his store too long...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10005800=いつまでも^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;を店の隅で震えたままにしておけないわ…
//[Reference] 'It all went well I hope?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10005900=上手くいったかしら？
//[Reference] 'How much was he cowering? Not at all? Well...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10006000=彼はどれくらい怯えてた？大丈夫だった？そっか…
//[Reference] 'I hope that means he's forgiven us at least...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10006100=少なくとも私たちを許してくれたってことだと良いんだけど…
//[Reference] 'I heard you went out of your way to insure the town so I can perform even bigger experiments!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10006200=私がもっと大きな実験ができるようにわざわざ町に保険をかけてくれたって聞いたわ！
//[Reference] 'I hope you'll accept these as a payment of sorts...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10006300=これつまらないものだけど受け取ってくれるといいな…
//[Reference] 'Look forward to my next experiment!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10006400=次の実験を楽しみにしていてちょうだいね！
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10006500=^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'I uh...may have another problem.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10006600=あの…別の問題が起きちゃったかも。
//[Reference] 'Don't worry though! I didn't almost blow ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; up this time...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10006700=でも心配しないでね！今回はギリギリで^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;を吹き飛ばしたりしてないから…
//[Reference] 'Oh, and in case you wondered, I also didn't successfully blow him up either.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10006800=まあ、あなたが気にしたところで、どっちにしろ吹き飛ばすこともできなかったわ。
//[Reference] 'This has absolutely nothing to do with ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; at all.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10006900=これは^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;とは全くこれっぽっちも全然関係ないわ。
//[Reference] 'Well...okay. So maybe it does. Just a little.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10007000=えーと…分かったわよ。まあ多分関係あるかも。ちょっとだけ。
//[Reference] 'But it's not really my fault. It's the ^c:1486b0;monster's^c:pop; fault...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10007100=でも本当に私のせいじゃないわ。^c:1486b0;モンスター^c:pop;のせいなのよ…
//[Reference] 'I only made it. I didn't tell it what to do!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10007200=私は作っただけよ。何かをしろとは言ってないわ！
//[Reference] 'But as soon as it came to life, it ran right out of the ^c:1486b0;lab^c:pop; and bumped into ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop;...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10007300=でも命を宿した途端、^c:1486b0;研究室^c:pop;を飛び出して^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;とばったり鉢合わせちゃったのよ…
//[Reference] 'I don't think I've ever seen anyone jump that high before in all my years.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10007400=あんなに高くジャンプした子なんて生まれて初めて見たわ。
//[Reference] 'If only I'd had my tools on hand to evaluate at the height at the time...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10007500=あの時、高さを測る道具を持ってさえいればなあ…
//[Reference] 'But that is a different regret entirely.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10007600=でも今回はそう言うことじゃなくてね。
//[Reference] 'For now, I need you to deliver another ^c:d03e37;gift^c:pop; to ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop;...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10007700=とりあえず、^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;に別の^c:d03e37;プレゼント^c:pop;を届けてほしいの…
//[Reference] 'You gave him the ^c:d03e37;gift^c:pop;? Well at least that's one weight off my mind...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10007800=^c:d03e37;プレゼント^c:pop;を渡してくれた？まあこれで少なくとも1つは不安が解消されたわ…
//[Reference] 'Now we just need to do something about ^c:1486b0;my creation^c:pop;...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10007900=どれじゃ今度は^c:1486b0;私の発明品^c:pop;をどうにかしないとね…
//[Reference] 'I'll give you my tracking device so you can track him down.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10008000=あの子を追跡できるように追跡装置を渡しておくわね。
//[Reference] 'Perhaps you'll have better luck convincing him to come back...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10008100=あの子に戻ってくるよう上手く説得してくれないかしら…
//[Reference] 'Just so you know, he's engineered to have a fondness for ^c:d03e37;candy^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10008200=あーそうそう、あの子は^c:d03e37;キャンディー^c:pop;を好むように設計してあるわ。
//[Reference] 'Please run that ^c:d03e37;gift^c:pop; on over to ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10008300=その^c:d03e37;プレゼント^c:pop;を^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;の所まで急いで届けてくれないかしら。
//[Reference] 'I was so used to having him hanging around all the time but I'm worried I've scared him off...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10008400=今回ばかりは彼を怖がらせちゃったかも…
//[Reference] 'You should be able to find ^c:1486b0;my creation^c:pop; on your map...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10008500=あなたの地図で^c:1486b0;私の発明品^c:pop;を見つけられるはずよ…
//[Reference] 'It might be worth keeping in mind that he's engineered to have a fondness for ^c:d03e37;candy^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10008600=あの子は^c:d03e37;キャンディー^c:pop;を好むように設計してあるから、覚えておくと良いかもね。
//[Reference] 'You managed to bring back ^c:1486b0;my creation^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10008700=^c:1486b0;私の発明品^c:pop;を連れ戻してきてくれたの？
//[Reference] 'Ah, thank you, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! You're really a miracle!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10008800=まあ、ありがとう、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！本当に奇跡だわ！
//[Reference] 'But now...somehow we still need to clean up this mess...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10008900=でも今は…なんとかしてこの混乱を収めないとね…
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;Max^c:pop; has been clamouring after us again...maybe you could start there?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10009000=^c:1486b0;マックス^c:pop;がまた私たちにカンカンだわ…どうにかしてくれるかしら？
//[Reference] 'We can't keep it? I feared as much...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10009100=置いておけないの？恐れていた通りだわ…
//[Reference] 'Do you think perhaps we might be able to sell it to one of the ^c:1486b0;merchants^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10009200=もしかしたら^c:1486b0;商人^c:pop;の誰かに売れないかしら？
//[Reference] 'I could certainly use the funds for my research...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10009300=私の研究資金に使えるかもしれないわね…
//[Reference] 'Perhaps you could go and discuss it with them?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10009400=彼らと相談してきてくれないかしら？
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;Max^c:pop; has been demanding to see us...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10009500=^c:1486b0;マックス^c:pop;が私たちとの面会を要求してきたわ…
//[Reference] 'Do you think you could go on my behalf?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10009600=私の代わりに行ってきてくれない？
//[Reference] 'No luck there, huh?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10009700=やっぱ駄目だった？
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; did send me a note while you were away though...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10009800=あなたがいない間に^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;がメモを送ってきたんだけど…
//[Reference] 'It seems like he's recovered a bit from the ordeal and it sounded like he might have an idea...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10009900=事故からは少し回復したみたいで、あとアイデアがあるらしいわ…
//[Reference] 'Do you think you could go find out what it is?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10010000=どんなアイデアか確かめに行ってきてくれないかしら？
//[Reference] 'I can't really risk leaving ^c:1486b0;my creation^c:pop; to run off again...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10010100=また逃がす危険を冒してまで^c:1486b0;私の発明品^c:pop;を残すことはできないわ…
//[Reference] 'Were any of the ^c:1486b0;merchants^c:pop; willing to take him?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10010200=あの子を快く引き取ってくれそうな^c:1486b0;商人^c:pop;はいた？
//[Reference] 'Have you talked to them about it yet?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10010300=彼らとはもう話をしたの？
//[Reference] 'Have you been to see ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; yet?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10010400=もう^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;には会ったかしら？
//[Reference] 'It sounds like he might have an idea what to do...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10010500=何かアイデアを持ってるらしいんだけど…
//[Reference] 'So what was ^c:1486b0;Leif's^c:pop; solution?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10010600=それで^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;の解決策って何だったの？
//[Reference] 'His ^c:1486b0;sister^c:pop;, was it?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10010700=彼の^c:1486b0;姉妹^c:pop;、ですって？
//[Reference] 'I would certainly like to meet her when she comes by to pick up ^c:1486b0;Frankie^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10010800=彼女が^c:1486b0;フランキー^c:pop;を引き取りに来たら是非会ってみたいわ！
//[Reference] 'We may not quite be done with our experiments yet, but I think now is the time to give you the reward!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10010900=まだ実験は終わってないんだけど、とりあえずあなたにはお礼をしておくわ！
//[Reference] 'Thank you for taking the time to help, none of the others would have put up with my experiments!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10011000=時間を割いてまで助けてくれてありがとう、私の実験に耐えてくれる人なんて他にいないもの！
//[Reference] 'Perhaps someday you'll agree to become a test subject! Or even a lab member!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10011100=いつかテストの被験者になってくれないかしら！それか研究室のメンバーでもいいわよ！
//[Reference] 'We could even move the lab into your home if you'd like!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10011200=あなたさえ良ければ、研究室をあなたの家に移すのもいいわね！
//[Reference] 'Just say the word!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10011300=遠慮なく言ってね！
//[Reference] 'Hm? I'm a little busy...right...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10011400=ん？今はちょっと忙しいんだけど…
//[Reference] 'Is...is that a robot?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10011500=それって…ロボット？
//[Reference] 'A robot I didn't make? Let me take a closer look!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10011600=他の人が作ったロボットなの？ちょっと良く見せて！
//[Reference] 'So...so lifelike! I would never have imagined such craftsmanship!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10011700=すごい…生きてるみたい！こんな職人技が存在するなんて！
//[Reference] 'It was responsive before? It's not just a doll? Incredible.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10011800=前は反応があったの？ただの人形じゃないんだ？すごい。
//[Reference] 'So... Can I have it?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10011900=これ…私にくれない？
//[Reference] 'No!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10012000=ダメ！
//[Reference] 'Aw. I thought of all people, you'd understand...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10012100=えー。これは科学の、全人類のためなのよ、あなたなら分かってくれると思ったのに…
//[Reference] 'Alright then. What did you want from me? I assume you didn't come just to tease me with this beauty?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10012200=分かったわよ。じゃあ何しに来たの？こんな逸品を見せびらかしに来たわけじゃないでしょ？
//[Reference] 'She's broken? Hm...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10012300=壊れてるの？ふむ…
//[Reference] 'No, I don't think that's the case. I suspect she's just out of fuel...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10012400=いや、違うわね。ただの燃料切れじゃないかなぁ…
//[Reference] '^c:d03e37;8 starbits^c:pop; should do it I think!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10012500=これなら^c:d03e37;スタービット8個^c:pop;あれば何とかなるわね！
//[Reference] 'Just bring them here and I think we can have her back up and running again, no problem.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10012600=それを持ってきてくれたら彼女を再起動できると思うわ。なんてことないわよ。
//[Reference] '^c:d03e37;8 starbits^c:pop; it was.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10012700=^c:d03e37;スタービット8個^c:pop;よ。
//[Reference] 'You should be able to find them at night. I don't think it'll prove too much trouble!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10012800=スタービットは夜に見つけられるの。そんな難しく考えなくても大丈夫よ！
//[Reference] 'Ah, great, perfect! Let me just take those off your hands.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10012900=おお、すごいじゃない、それよそれ！それじゃあ私にちょうだい。
//[Reference] 'Well now...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10013000=えーとそれで…
//[Reference] 'Not even a thanks?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10013100=お礼もないの？
//[Reference] 'And here I had so many questions to ask...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10013200=それに聞きたいことが山ほどあるんだけど…
//[Reference] 'I guess you'll probably want to hurry after her!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10013300=とりあえず急いであの子を追いかけましょう！
//[Reference] 'Hm, what are these?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10013400=ふーむ、何これ？
//[Reference] 'I suppose these are my thanks for helping revive her?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10013500=あの子を復活させたお礼ってやつ？
//[Reference] 'Thank you, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;, for delivering them!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10013600=わざわざ届けてくれたのね、ありがとう^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'Uh...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10013700=えーっと…
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;, I think I made a mistake...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10013800=^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;、ちょっとミスっちゃったかも…
//[Reference] 'Those items you gave me...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10013900=あなたにもらったアイテムなんだけど…
//[Reference] 'The letter told me to do something with the ^c:d03e37;device^c:pop; and then place it in ^c:1486b0;Leif's store^c:pop;...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10014000=手紙には、^c:d03e37;装置^c:pop;は^c:1486b0;レイフの店^c:pop;に置けって書いてあって…
//[Reference] 'Naturally...I let curiosity get the better of me. I really just wanted to see what would happen!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10014100=つい…好奇心にかられちゃって。だって何が起こるか確かめてみたかったんだもん！
//[Reference] 'Now ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; has disappeared and I don't dare go near the place...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10014200=そしたら^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;が消えちゃって、怖くて近付く勇気も出ないわ…
//[Reference] 'Could you...could you go take a look for me? I left the ^c:d03e37;device^c:pop; in the ^c:d03e37;cash register^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10014300=お願い…代わりに様子を見てきて？^c:d03e37;装置^c:pop;は^c:d03e37;レジ^c:pop;の所に置いたままよ。
//[Reference] 'Did you find it?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10014400=装置はあった？
//[Reference] 'It should be in the ^c:d03e37;cash register^c:pop;...I think.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10014500=^c:d03e37;レジ^c:pop;の所にある…はずなんだけど。
//[Reference] 'Ah... Yeah...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10014600=ああ…それよ…
//[Reference] 'That's the one.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10014700=その装置だわ。
//[Reference] 'Based on what I saw when it activated, I think it's some sort of teleportation device.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10014800=起動した時の様子から察するに、転送装置だと思うの。
//[Reference] 'I should be able to modify it to send you wherever it took him!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10014900=これにちょっと手を加えれば、あなたをレイフのいる場所に転送できるはずよ！
//[Reference] 'Then you can find him and bring him back!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10015000=それで彼を見つけて連れ戻してきて！
//[Reference] 'There! That should do it!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10015100=ほら！完成！
//[Reference] 'Just activate it and it'll whisk you away!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10015200=あとは起動すれば転移できるわ！
//[Reference] 'I would love to go myself, but I need to remain here and observe.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10015300=私も行きたいけど、ここに残って様子を見ていなくちゃ。
//[Reference] 'For science, you know?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10015400=科学のために、ね？
//[Reference] 'Just activate it and it'll whisk you away!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10015500=起動すれば転移できるわ！
//[Reference] 'I would love to go myself, but I need to remain here and observe.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10015600=私も行きたいけど、ここに残って様子を見ていなくちゃ。
//[Reference] 'For science, you know?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10015700=科学のために、ね？
//[Reference] 'Did you find it?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10015800=装置はあった？
//[Reference] 'It should be in the ^c:d03e37;cash register^c:pop;...I think.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10015900=^c:d03e37;レジ^c:pop;の所にある…はずなんだけど。
//[Reference] 'Oh, hi ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10016000=あら、こんにちは^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'Hm? That teleportation device? It wasn't supposed to be recoverable?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10016100=え？あの転送装置？本当は修理できるものじゃなかったの？
//[Reference] 'Don't underestimate the power of science!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10016200=科学の力をナメないで！
//[Reference] 'Naturally I improved upon it and developed something better!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10016300=当然、改良を加えて性能も上げてやったわよ！
//[Reference] 'I think ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; is going to be pretty pleased when he sees these...'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10016400=^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;が見たらすごく喜ぶでしょうね…
//[Reference] 'Hi ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! What do you have there?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10016500=あら、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！何を持ってるの？
//[Reference] 'Those ^c:d03e37;fragments^c:pop; are just what I need for my latest experiment!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10016600=何その^c:d03e37;欠片^c:pop;、ちょうど新しい実験に使えそうじゃない！
//[Reference] 'Oh... you want me to repair that teleporter?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10016700=なんだ…そのテレポーターを修理してほしいの？
//[Reference] 'Alright, I could do that... But I'm positive you would've liked my experiment!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10016800=分かったわ、できる…けど、私の実験も気に入ってくれたはずよ！
//[Reference] 'Fine... I'll need you to bring me some materials before I can repair this though.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10016900=まあいいわ…でも、修理する前に材料をいくつか持って来てほしいの。
//[Reference] 'I could try it without them. But I don't think ^c:1486b0;Max^c:pop; would be please if I caused any more accidents.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10017000=材料がなくてもできるけど、これ以上事故を起こしたら^c:1486b0;マックス^c:pop;が喜ばないでしょうね。
//[Reference] 'He might take my license away again!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10017100=また許可証を没収されちゃうかもしれないし！
//[Reference] 'Oh... ^c:1486b0;Max^c:pop; is missing? And this teleporter would take us to him?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10017200=あらら…^c:1486b0;マックス^c:pop;がいなくなっちゃったの？で、このテレポーターで彼のところに行けるのね？
//[Reference] 'I mean... Maybe we can wait until I'm finished with a few other...  projects?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10017300=ってことは…他のプロジェクトが終わるまで待っててもらっても…いいかな？
//[Reference] 'There's no harm in a slight delay, right?'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10017400=ちょっとくらい遅くなっても大丈夫でしょ？
//[Reference] 'No... you're right.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10017500=ダメ…だよね、やっぱ。
//[Reference] 'If you can bring me ^c:d03e37;6 starbits^c:pop;? That ought to be enough, I think.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10017600=^c:d03e37;スタービットを6個^c:pop;を持って来てくれる？それで足りると思うわ。
//[Reference] 'Ah, you've got the ^c:d03e37;starbits^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10017700=あぁ、^c:d03e37;スタービット^c:pop;を持ってきてくれたのね！
//[Reference] 'This should do the trick. Be sure to let ^c:1486b0;Max^c:pop; know that I helped!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10017800=これで上手くいくはずよ。私が手伝ったってことをちゃんと^c:1486b0;マックス^c:pop;に伝えてよね！
//[Reference] 'That teleporter is good to go! You should use it to find ^c:1486b0;Max^c:pop;! And be sure to let him know that I helped!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10017900=テレポーターの準備はできたわ！これを使って^c:1486b0;マックス^c:pop;を見つけて！あと、私が手伝ったってことをちゃんと伝えてね！
//[Reference] '^c:d03e37;6 starbits^c:pop; it was.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10018000=^c:d03e37;スタービット6個^c:pop;よ。
//[Reference] 'They still turn up at night! I'm sure you will do this effortlessly again.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10018100=スタービットは夜に現れるわ！またすぐに見つけられるはずよ。
//[Reference] 'That ^c:1486b0;Teleporter^c:pop; the other day, I think I've found a way to recreate it quite easily.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10018200=この前の^c:1486b0;テレポーター^c:pop;だけど、簡単に複製できる方法を見つけたのよ。
//[Reference] 'Just needs the correct ingredients.'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10018300=正しい材料が必要なだけ。
//[Reference] 'The device is probably stable enough, but you never know when you lose it!'
staxel.village.dialogue.ScientistPrimary.line:10018400=装置は安定してると思うけど、いつ不安定になってもおかしくないから気を付けてね！
